  "title": "All-Party Parliamentary Group on Global Deforestation",
  "purpose": "To provide a cross-party forum to discuss and promote greater awareness of the impacts of global deforestation, for communities, the climate, for nature and human rights. The APPG will consider the UK’s role in contributing to global deforestation, as well as considering UK and international approaches to addressing global deforestation.",
